                       "description":  "\u003cb\u003eGandalf\u003c/b\u003e is the grey pilgrim, a wanderer of hidden roads and quiet counsel.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eHe walks the edge between shadow and hope, guiding the small and the humble because he knows their courage can outlast any sword.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eHe trusts in patience, in wisdom earned by travel, and in the spark that lights when others have given in to fear.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe Shire lies under his watch, and the first steps of his journey begin among its green lanes, where he gathers trusted companions, listens for the first uneasy rumors, and searches old ground for relics that have waited too long.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eHis path starts in quiet places, but it will not remain quiet.",
